00:22:12.200 --> 00:22:16.640
influential mentors in your career and
and what kind of advice did they give

00:22:16.640 --> 00:22:18.100
you as you moved along?

00:22:18.100 --> 00:22:21.529
KAGAN: Well I think at
Princeton, I'll start with Princeton.

00:22:21.529 --> 00:22:25.640
In Princeton it was my senior thesis
adviser who maybe is here, Sean Wilentz.

00:22:25.640 --> 00:22:30.559
